{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020/05/trigonometric-function","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"saitoxu.io","siteUrl":"https://saitoxu.io"}},"ogp":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAjElEQVQoz82STQoDIQyF5/5HUVcuFNfeRdyIohvx7xWFllJm2llMaQOPhJiEj8QNF9v21YFjjIc/o+eeQ8LXgne2V7tLWGtFSgnWWhhjVhxjRM4Z3vul3vtnwvujcw6UUhBCoJQCYwxCCEgpobUG5xwhhPMDpy+lLIqpSdxaW4QzP+Pf7vDSK//dx74BXyBi+B0nsZEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=","width":1200,"height":630,"src":"/static/bb302f3ca7aabb14b0ae74df1c534526/e7e81/ogp.png","srcSet":"/static/bb302f3ca7aabb14b0ae74df1c534526/e7e81/ogp.png 1x"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4c02d162-c06d-5665-9657-dfa24ada6d5f","excerpt":"AtCoder Beginner Contest 168のC問題で\n余弦定理を使う必要があり、調べるのにけっこう時間使ったので関連する公式等を復習しておく。 ついでにgatsby-remark-katexを導入してKaTeX…","html":"<p>AtCoder Beginner Contest 168の<a href=\"https://atcoder.jp/contests/abc168/tasks/abc168_c\">C問題</a>で\n余弦定理を使う必要があり、調べるのにけっこう時間使ったので関連する公式等を復習しておく。</p>\n<p>ついでに<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-remark-katex/\">gatsby-remark-katex</a>を導入してKaTeXで数式を書けるようにした。</p>\n<h2>ラジアン・度数法の相互変換</h2>\n<p>ラジアンと度数単位は以下の関係になる。</p>\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>π</mi><mtext> </mtext><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">r</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>18</mn><msup><mn>0</mn><mo>∘</mo></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\pi\\,\\mathrm{rad}=180^\\circ</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">π</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">r</span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">a</span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">d</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.724115em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\">8</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.724115em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mbin mtight\">∘</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n<p>Pythonだと以下のように相互変換できる。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> math\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># ラジアン => 度数</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>degrees<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 90.0</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>degrees<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 59.99999999999999</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>degrees<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 29.999999999999996</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 度数 => ラジアン</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>radians<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">90</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 0.5</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>radians<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">60</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 0.3333333333333333</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>radians<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 0.16666666666666666</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>三角関数の公式</h2>\n<h3>三角関数</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 300px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e4eab80493a73381ea63d02a2e36abca/56b05/fig1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fig1\"\n        title=\"fig1\"\n        src=\"/static/e4eab80493a73381ea63d02a2e36abca/56b05/fig1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e4eab80493a73381ea63d02a2e36abca/7237a/fig1.jpg 148w,\n/static/e4eab80493a73381ea63d02a2e36abca/0cfdf/fig1.jpg 295w,\n/static/e4eab80493a73381ea63d02a2e36abca/56b05/fig1.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi></mfrac><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>b</mi><mi>c</mi></mfrac><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\sin \\theta=\\cfrac{a}{c}, \\cos\\theta=\\cfrac{b}{c}, \\tan\\theta=\\cfrac{a}{b}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">sin</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.276em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.5899999999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">c</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.74em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">a</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">cos</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.276em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.5899999999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">c</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.74em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">b</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">tan</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.276em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.5899999999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">b</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.74em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">a</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n<p>Pythonでは以下のように扱う。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> math\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># sinを求める(引数はラジアン)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sin<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 1.0</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># cos</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cos<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => -1.0</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># tan</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tan<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 1.633123935319537e+16</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># sinからラジアンを求める</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>asin<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 0.5</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># acos</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>acos<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 1.0</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># atan</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>atan<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># => 0.25</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>正弦定理</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 300px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e867f54f6bc7eae2fd26d6f824d5f0ca/56b05/fig2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 103.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fig2\"\n        title=\"fig2\"\n        src=\"/static/e867f54f6bc7eae2fd26d6f824d5f0ca/56b05/fig2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e867f54f6bc7eae2fd26d6f824d5f0ca/7237a/fig2.jpg 148w,\n/static/e867f54f6bc7eae2fd26d6f824d5f0ca/0cfdf/fig2.jpg 295w,\n/static/e867f54f6bc7eae2fd26d6f824d5f0ca/56b05/fig2.jpg 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>A</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>b</mi><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>B</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>c</mi><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\cfrac{a}{\\sin A} = \\cfrac{b}{\\sin B} = \\cfrac{c}{\\sin C} = 2R</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.276em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.5899999999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mop\">sin</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">A</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.74em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">a</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></spa